      <title>富国银行的纳尔逊预计到 2025 年底 10 年期债券收益率将低于 4%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-26/wells-fargo-s-nelson-sees-10-year-yield-below-4-by-end-of-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国银行宏观策略师埃里克·尼尔森 (Erik Nelson) 讨论了 10 年期收益率，并表示到明年年底收益率可能会跌破 4%。他与 Sonali Basak 就“彭博实际收益率”进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-26/wells-fargo-s-nelson-sees-10-year-yield-below-4-by-end-of-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 18:03:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
